In this episode, Shai shares his life journey, marked by critical decisions that shaped his research career and path in life.
His message to students is inspiring and practical: “Being a student is an excellent opportunity to open your eyes and mind and discover what you love to do. Stay curious and experiment in different labs.”</p>

